chapter:
&reftitle.setup;




 &reftitle.required;


  This module uses the functions of zlib
  by Jean-loup Gailly and Mark Adler.
  As of PHP 8.4.0, the minimum zlib version required is 1.2.11.
  Prior to PHP 8.4.0, the minimum zlib version required was 1.2.0.4.





&reference.zlib.configure;



&reference.zlib.ini;





 &reftitle.resources;


  This extension defines a file pointer resource returned by
  gzopen.
  Prior to PHP 8.0.0, zlib.deflate and zlib.inflate
  resources were also defined.
